Hope this email finds you well.

Kindly give us your best quote for attached Inquiry, lead time and 
payment terms.

Would it be possible to set up a video call in the near future to 
discuss this project?

Appreciate your response at the earliest.

Thanks and best regards,

Andy Liu

Sales Manager, Middle East & South Asia Market
